e><br />\n嘩巴打你點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係絲打 運輸邊有計"},{"pid":"ad56be079bbc9fd1e35e6f3a1215a46ddce64700","tid":280241,"uid":64389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩個星期四張on9</blockquote><br />\n嘩巴打你點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依排仲多左好多雷射"},{"pid":"683fa98d94dea26b60141bbc27399348de5d265c","tid":280241,"uid":117689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:15:06.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2244ead34cd818216d55848a1841e51677c8883","tid":280241,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前石硤尾南山村道D車泊街好耐都冇抄<br />\n今朝返工經過, 7點幾已經有幾架車車頭sip左牛肉乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係今年抄得勁左<br />\n都岩既, 你唔抄得勁, d港豬會好放肆, 真係泊到阻哂街<br />\n為左自己方便</blockquote><br />\n其實上年年頭開始。<br />\n<br />\n有一排黑警專登放風話唔會警告唔會等就抄。（果排連工廠區都勁密）<br />\n果期報哂數抄多左幾多張。<br />\n放幾次風，到左今年連風都唔放， 整體抄得密左好多。<br />\n<br />\n相比2年前， 有次黑警會企一陣先，等你走。<br />\n仲有次黑警會專登去附近餐廳講聲會抄牌提人走 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0734df22ea2dba064a12233038045527057bf4a","tid":280241,"uid":64389,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚有咁多錶位你泊"},{"pid":"8d4a01360557718c98ed3f1862067b89a7ccd5da","tid":280241,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:20:00.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bd8bb00aa2f66fe0dd81faf79f6c8ac031a85f","tid":280241,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockq