s/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n咁........點解過鐘都唔入錶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明知兩個鐘內返唔到黎, 就泊入停車場啦</blockquote><br />\nChing有冇車<br />\n有車嘅話有冇出過街</blockquote><br />\n日日都要渣車返工放工<br />\n如果我想泊一泊街, 但唔肯定趕唔趕到返黎入錶<br />\n我寧願唔泊錶位, 泊無黃線地方<br />\n<br />\n已經好多次, 遲左入錶比人抄, 但係前後唔泊錶位無事<br />\n<br />\n就係因為中過幾次招, 所以就話比大家知, 趕唔切入錶唔係藉口, 係抵死"},{"pid":"14c2b6e7d029d08fae296bb9d305b90a8ee7d357","tid":280241,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"過去一年幾乎全年都無三張<br />\n<br />\n單單係今個月食左兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊得15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e4d5f008736cec058256d1b486873f941da392","tid":280241,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過去一年幾乎全年都無三張<br />\n<br />\n單單係今個月食左兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊得15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到明而家會喪抄wow, 無睇新聞架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋而家好多投訴撚. 泊得街真係預左抄."},{"pid":"b9edf82e7f24a952310ce8640afdf96ac3fadf4f","tid":280241,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:22:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dec483dd597913a57848016653903058204bc38a","tid":280241,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家抄牌320定450？</blockquote><br />\n仲係320"},{"pid":"779f71e8bbd277600faca9f5e52c5f0574b7e55b","tid":280241,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過去一年幾乎全年都無三張<br />\n<br />\n單單係今個月食左兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊得15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到明而家會喪抄wow, 無睇新聞架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋而家好多投訴撚. 泊得街真係預左抄.</blockquote><br />\n係, 呢排好撚多投訴撚<br />\n有次試過見到阿SIR係我車前面, 拿拿聲沖過去<br />\n阿Sir話, 你黎就好啦, 我抄到手軟, 由3點鐘開始有人不停投訴, 到而家8點<br />\n都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n連續投訴左3日, 之後我見散仔再拖多個白衫黎, 抄完成條街, 再望上樓上, 可能搵邊條仆街投訴<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢班投訴既人, 似係玩警犬多過駕駛者"},{"pid":"6d9927719514a81c92981ea480c558487cdc6c10","tid":280241,"uid":19917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"唔好再講，26尋日拍出界小小都食一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827eed7c400028a493448e599d4357776250e14","tid":280241,"uid":19917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好再講，26尋日拍出界小小都食一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自膠 泊出界"},{"pid":"0e4eaaf43fd8e352a51fe513306609e7f4d970bc","tid":280241,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:26:48.000Z","msg":"請清洪打官司唔駛錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c516d8392a5042e23de107b0cbc946778f207d62","tid":280241,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好再講，26尋日拍出界小小都食一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自膠 泊出界</blockquote><br />\n呢排都有26既朋友比人抄左, 佢話一年都唔中一張"},{"pid":"3225a78361dcce31fba3797a2ec5eb72fc830855","tid":280241,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3248e04e93ea1434601d1cdbfaf6ac980ee83c32","tid":280241,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"聽聞有D司機想泊街點知滿哂冇得泊就會打電話叫差念黎抄牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aae974538c618cf370d47bcedecdfcb63f